Package: weatherR
Title: Allows you to access current weather and next 4 days weather data in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: "Abrar Wafa <abrarwafa89@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Access worldweatheronline.com to check for today's or the next
    four days' weather conditions (i.e tempreture, chances of rain), and let
    you know if you can go hiking on that day
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    RCurl,
    rjson,
    assertthat
License: CC0
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
